{"tid":2333822,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"其實都估唔到阿仙奴搞成甘","createTime":"2020-12-20T17:24:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T19:09:49.000Z","uid":309376,"like":7,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"18b3ef6c035fe486eca3dc02a6e69a3a90e36b75","tid":2333822,"uid":309376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T17:24:01.000Z","msg":"當年不敗，之後星散，雲加玩幼齒，年年季尾爭四，8:2後玩番即食，雲加下台，開始無得跟歐聯，歐霸都就快無得踢，分分鐘降班。 以上的事情只不過係十幾年內的事 由爭標份子變撚到要護級 雖然我唔係阿迷 不過都覺得幾傷感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7329c1e6882c43902ab90a108d1cdac9894bf6d1","tid":2333822,"uid":89037,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T17:24:57.000Z","msg":"反雲<br />\n自食其果<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5b198e77780574749975b57a95db1a61d6818f7","tid":2333822,"uid":12911,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T17:33:34.000Z","msg":"利都試過俾學臣搞 轉個頭買中so7都可以爭標啦"},{"pid":"cd530062ed3bc1a3dca712d31623ff19e29b16b6","tid":2333822,"uid":76804,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T17:58:36.000Z","msg":"同香港一樣"},{"pid":"584abe11da18df8980aff87b68acd8bea2f9706d","tid":2333822,"uid":31215,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"7329c1e6882c43902ab90a108d1cdac9894bf6d1","tid":2333822,"uid":89037,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T17:24:57.000Z","msg":"反雲<br />\n自食其果<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T18:50:48.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n以為年年第四好失禮<br />\n都唔睇下對手咩料，自己有幾多budget 同啲隊波咩料<br />\n日撚日怨歐聯16朗又年年第四<br />\n而家反完雲<br />\n冇撚埋要護級<br />\n完全係反雲自己造成"},{"pid":"ff462ea06c0bca75d0fb9f28c92b42001fb6a089","tid":2333822,"uid":167509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T18:53:29.000Z","msg":"反雲乏術"},{"pid":"938513bf1